<h1>Registration Information</h1>

<h2>Steps to Register</h2>

<p>Complete and sign all areas of the registration and health form. Use a separate form for each camper you are registering.</p>

<p><b>Online:</b> Register Now! (Click to register and pay through a secure site)</p> <!--Link to online registration-->

<p><b>Deliver:</b>	Visitors Center Office, 5739 Old Lansing Road; Hours: Tuesday - Saturday, 10 a.m. - 5 p.m. Sunday, Noon - 4 p.m.</p>

<p><b>Fax:</b> (517) 322-9394 Attn: Registrar; Faxed registrations must include Visa or MasterCard number </p>

<p><b>Mail:</b>	Attn: Registrar Woldumar Nature Center 5739 Old Lansing Rd. Lansing, MI 48917 </p>

<p>Registration must be submitted with a $30 non-refundable deposit for each week of camp. Balance must be paid in full 7 days before the camp session. Full payment must be included if registering less than 7 days before the camp session.</p>

